{
  "stem": "22840.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The [HEBREW], the-- the Jewish military organization of the [HEBREW] of the Jewish agency, organized illegal entry.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were organized such illegal entry in the most intriguing way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is a story I was told.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I never checked its accuracy, but I have no reason to doubt it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And if the details are not exact, the-- the gist is exact, because it happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a British-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was a Czechoslovak brigade fighting under the British army in the Second World War.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That is a fact.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "After the war, somebody had the idea that all these soldiers would visit the Holy Land.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They got permission to do so.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The [HEBREW] bought all these permissions, structured families according to the permissions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one day we-- we were put on a train and went to Prague, stayed a couple of days in Prague, continued with the train to Marseille, France.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In Marseilles, we boarded a French ship called The French ship sailed through the Mediterranean to Alexandria and then docked in Haifa, where everybody went down, but nobody came back.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So there was an illegal legal-illegal [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Somebody paid a lot of money, because all these people, all these tourists brought furniture with them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So-- but anyway, that's how we got there in 1947.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was part of that group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother got a-- some kind of husband, which was too young to have me as a-- as a child.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as I said, it was just pro forma.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "June.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "June.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "June, 1947.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a family, just the two of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
